HEADWORD: Boat shell
<hw>Boat" shell`</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>. <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <sd>(a)</sd>
<def>A marine gastropod of the genus <gen>Crepidula</gen>. The species
are numerous. It is so named from its form and interior deck.</def>
<sd>(b)</sd> <def>A marine univalve shell of the genus
<gen>Cymba</gen>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Boatsman</ent>⟦br⟧
